If you actually want to win the Zotac game do the following.

Open 10 tabs minimum trying to hit the Login page

https://www.zotacstore.com/us/customer/account/login/


Once you get logged in on 1 tab, close all other tabs. Then add to cart.

Once in cart, you need to start the paypal checkout process. OPEN THIS LINK IN 10 TABS AND REFRESH TILL IT WORKS!

https://store.zotac.com/paypal/express/start/

Fill out your Paypal info, hit continue. Once you see the URL bar say https://store.zotac.com/paypal/express/review/ you can open this page in as many tabs as you want till you see the checkout screen. Once you are at the checkout screen, make sure you have a shipping method selected and hit "Place Order".

Good luck!
